content.description: Stand start on low block, use undercling and crimps to strenuously topout.  Careful of block below topout.
content.location:
This is outside on the north wall in the little rock alcove far down in Twin Valley North.  "B3" on this map:   

A -The Complex   Twin Valley North B1- cold dinner etc B2 - Life on the Prarie B3 - A cool alcove of boulders set off of main cliff. 4 possible lines at best. Mostly V1-V2   C - Twin Valley Campground E - Barrel Ridge F - Alpine Bouldering Club G - Barrel Boulders H - Small ridge line. Maybe 5 problems possible, mostly short V1-V2. ?? - area to be explored?
